title: Spaghetti Bolognese
instructions: Cook spaghetti according to package instructions.
Heat olive oil in a pan, add chopped onions and garlic, and sauté until translucent.
Add minced beef and cook until browned.
Pour in canned tomatoes, season with salt and pepper, and simmer for 20 minutes.
Serve sauce over cooked spaghetti.

title: Poke Bowl
instructions: Cook sushi rice according to package instructions and let it cool.
In a bowl, mix soy sauce, sesame oil, and rice vinegar to make the dressing.
In serving bowls, layer the rice, diced tuna, avocado slices, and cucumber slices.
Drizzle with the dressing and garnish with sesame seeds.
